abstract: A new regression based approach is proposed for modeling marketing databases. 
    The approach is Bayesian and provides a number of significant improvements 
    over current methods. Independent variables can enter into the model in either 
    a parametric or nonparametric manner, significant variables can be identified 
    from a large number of potential regressors and an appropriate transformation 
    of the dependent variable can be automatically selected from a discrete set of 
    pre-specified candidate transformations.
